original: Cederberg, Ernst Gunnar, tandläkare, Skara, f. 4/10/01 i Ystad av urmak. Anders C. o. Karin Pehrsson. G. 29 m. farm. kand. Greta Bergqvist. Barn: Ake f. 30, Lars 33. — Stud:ex. i Ys’tad 20, farm. kand. 24, tandl :kand. 25, tandl. 28. Aman. o. assist, v. tandl linst. tandfylln :avd. 27-28, prakt, i Skara sed. 28.
translated: Cederberg, Ernst Gunnar, dentist, Skara, b. 4/10/01 in Ystad to clockmaker Anders C. and Karin Pehrsson. Married in 1929 to agronomy student Greta Bergqvist. Children: Ake born in 1930, Lars in 1933. He graduated high school in Ystad in 1920, became a graduate of agronomy in 1924, and a graduate of dentistry in 1925, then practiced as an apprentice and assistant in the dental filling department from 1927-1928. He began his own practice in Skara in 1928.
